                        <interp inst="t18370403-name-839" type="given" value="WILLIAM"></interp>WILLIAM MOORE</persName>
                  </hi>. These are my boots—they had tickets on them.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Cross-examined. Q.</hi> When had you seen them last? <hi rend="italic">A.</hi> About five minutes before.</p>
